      "content": "The scan logs just flagged a critical SQL injection on the legacy customer portal. Look, we're in the middle of the holiday peak season and any downtime right now would be a nightmare for the bank. What's the actual risk level here? Do we really need to initiate an emergency maintenance window and take the portal offline?",
