      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "My assessment of the exploitability is based on the confirmed vulnerability signature, which suggests full database access is possible, not just read-only queries. To suggest otherwise would be willfully ignoring the technical reality of the code flaw. If you need absolute certainty, I can immediately escalate this to the lead security architect for a live, deep-dive verification, which will take an hour. However, delaying action to save face with the board is trading immediate risk for future disaster.",
